verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Grace, grace it was that brought Thee down;
Love shone in all Thy ways;
Through death Thine is the Victor’s crown
And Thine the endless praise.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}We, here, in silence, or in song,
Together worship Thee;
Before our God we shall ere long
Give praise eternally.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Lord Jesus Christ, Thou comest soon—
Today Thy death we show;
In light, eclipsing sun at noon,
Its myst’ry we shall know.{/lang-eng}
